Class StackDataSet

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Double>, java.util.Collection<java.lang.Double>, java.util.List<java.lang.Double>, java.util.RandomAccess

    public class StackDataSet
extends java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.Double>
    Represents a value set for a Stack graph.

    Stack graphs have labels that are defined separately and each StackDataSet represents a "line" in the stack graph.

    Each StackDataSet can have a HTML color hex.
